7:36:48.000Z","msg":"講風涼話就叻，夠膽去美國啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22435f8521e196d35e7a20375249ebdd7e22f6c5","tid":2201905,"uid":289978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T07:41:08.000Z","msg":"美國財政部公布制裁11名中港官員包括特首林鄭月娥，指控他們執行北京政策，破壞香港民主、自治，並把其罪行一一指出。<br />\n<br />\n李家超（63歲）<br />\n<br />\n職位：保安局局長、港區國安委成員<br />\n<br />\n罪狀：作為保安局局長，李家超負責香港所有保安事宜。李家超也是行政會議成員（編註：行政會議是香港最高決策機構），有份協助特首制定政策，李在警隊內成立新部門，專責實施港版國安法，包括蒐集情報和進行調查。他參與制定和執行港版國安法，並涉及以國安法名義脅迫、逮捕、拘押香港市民。"},{"pid":"51c4508fa543d865756db1719db397633e6423f5","tid":2201905,"uid":44646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T07:42:47.000Z","msg":"孫中山、毛澤東都勾結外國勢力"},{"pid":"c3b28136d98d1cec04c1c5a1d99a48d2a5f208c7","tid":2201905,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T07:43:33.000Z","msg":"李匪家超 (受制裁人仕) 講既野有說服力嗎"},{"pid":"489dc80fd9eedb4ddacd0eed6f98151e155ce4a5","tid":2201905,"uid":54579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"51c4508fa543d865756db1719db397633e6423f5","tid":2201905,"uid":44646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T07:42:47.000Z","msg":"孫中山、毛澤東都勾結外國勢力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T07:46:07.000Z","msg":"勾結日本鬼子"},{"pid":"589168ced93a80a6422e5292ce0baf70ee375471","tid":2201905,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T07:49:24.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">屌你老母冚家超</span></span>"},{"pid":"4be9314466bd0b4a268f9587b9bc98cebc969323","tid":2201905,"uid":21141,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T07:50:45.000Z","msg":"雖然成個政府都好撚黑人憎<br />\n但係李家超係我心目中絕對係第一位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcde1073a2c5344236de6ac667758dd37d4a4626","tid":2201905,"uid":345502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb82d59653338e9dfbfee9dd402abdce4cd001da","ti